Phew... I never expected to find a dragon in such
a small room.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 3

But we managed to defeat it, didn't we?

(Amelia may not be back to normal, but her magical
power has increased)
スキット 表情 アメリ f 19
I can't help but be curious, after all?
No... It's fine. I'm focused on the battle.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 3
(Amelia still likes me as I am...)

スキット 表情 オリビア f 1
スキット スライドイン オリビア f 左
I think this is the student council room.
スキット 表情 オリビア f 7
I have documents related to the student council.
スキット 表情 オリビア f 6

Old documents... but there are signs that they
have been used recently.
Indeed. There isn't much dust on it.

(Could it be that they are extracting Leviathan's
magic power here?)
(But there doesn't seem to be any such device)
スキット 表情 オリビア f 13

What is it... Martin was supposed to be from a
famous lineage of magicians, right?
スキット 表情 オリビア f 1
This person is the last student council president.
スキット 表情 オリビア f 7

The person who reformed the academy and was called
a hero.
skit フェードアウト オリビア f

If it's the last... then there might be some
secret about the student council president written
here.

The fulfillment of my long-cherished wish, I
entrust it to my descendants.

If I can obtain the power of demons, I will be
able to stand at the pinnacle of the magical
world... no, the world.

If I can obtain the power of demons... this person
is Leviathan.

(Did the last student council president capture
Leviathan and extract her magical power?)
(But that person died a long time ago)

Hey, over here we have a lot of research papers
about demons.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 6
スキット スライドイン アメリ f 右2
Could it be that you were researching demons?
スキット 表情 オリビア f 1
スキット スライドイン オリビア f 左

It's highly possible. The last student council
president was breaking taboos, huh?
スキット 表情 オリビア f 9

The remaining documents belong to Casbard Martin,
don't they?

(So... if the descendant of the Martin family
enrolled, it means they would continue the
research)

(If that's the case, it would explain why
Leviathan occasionally has her magical power
extracted)

(Because it can only be done when the descendant
is enrolled)

(If that's the case, it means there are still
people from the Martin family here...)
I never expected to make it this far.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 6
スキット スライドイン アメリ f 右2
My voice... is being carried by magic.
スキット 表情 オリビア f 6
スキット スライドイン オリビア f 左
Someone was watching us. Who could it be?
I am the student council president.
スキット 表情 オリビア f 1

There is no student council president at Caledonia
Magic Academy.

Strictly speaking, only someone from the Martin
family can become the student council president.

The claim of it being abolished is a lie. In
secret, someone from the Martin family has been
assuming the position every time they enroll.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 1
What on earth is this for?

I can't say anymore. You'll have to investigate it
yourself.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 8
スキット 表情 オリビア f 7

In that case, are you a member of the Martin
family?
But it shouldn't be on the roster.

Koushin Masamune... You've managed to find your
way here.
But this is where it ends.
I will definitely win in the end.
スキット 表情 アメリ f 1

It's a waste to throw away valuable materials, but
there's no other choice.
You all should disappear as well.

The room is overflowing with magical energy...
スキット 表情 オリビア f 8
I intend to blow up the entire room.
